com.canoo.dolphin.impl

Class BeanRepositoryImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.canoo.dolphin.impl.BeanRepositoryImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BeanRepository

    public class BeanRepositoryImpl
extends Object
implements BeanRepository
    A BeanRepository keeps a list of all registered Dolphin Beans and the mapping between OpenDolphin IDs and the associated Dolphin Bean. A new bean needs to be registered with the registerBean(Object, PresentationModel, UpdateSource) method and can be deleted with the delete(Object) method.
